cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel data augmentation method for automatic speech recognition using neural text-to-encoder model. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech signals and acoustic features. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of pre-trained E2E-ASR encoder and retraining of E2E-ASR decoder. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a machine learning technique for improving ASR performance. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing of speech signals and acoustic features.
